Struggle for U.S. troop pullout 
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Pyongyang, October 8 (KCNA) -- The south headquarters of the National Alliance for the Country's Reunification reportedly made public a statement on October 3 on the occasion of the first anniversary of the declared "Day of the Nation."
   The statement said the declaration of "Day of the Nation" was a declaration of the vigorous struggle of the 70 million fellow countrymen in the north, south and abroad to reunify the country through great national unity without fail, always cherishing the fact that they are descendants of king Tangun's nation though they live separated from each other.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
   The struggle is gaining momentum to defend the sovereignty of the nation and reunify the country by the great unity of the whole nation, it noted, and said: &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
   Though suffering from the temporary division in the 5,000-year long history of the nation, we have the great platform of national reunification and the united driving forces. So the reunification is sure to come true when we fight upholding the banner of national independence and patriotism. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
   We will unite ourselves firmly under the banner of national independence and great unity and do our utmost to get the U.S. Forces, sources of all evils, withdrawn and the "National Security Law" against reunification and nation, repealed.

Paper on war preparations in S. Korea
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Pyongyang, October 8 (KCNA) -- Rodong Sinmun today comments on the South Korean authorities' criminal effort to kill fellow countrymen in concert with foreign forces.
   Among the fund the South Korean authorities paid for the upkeep of the U.S. imperialist aggressor forces in South Korea last year, the indirect fees amounted to 1,800 billion won. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
   They plan to import 110 sophisticated ground-to-ground missiles and uptodate sea observation and information systems from the united states with a colossal amount of money allegedly to cope with "threat" from the north. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
   The news analyst says: &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
   This is an unpardonable criminal act to unleash war against the north with the backing of their American masters. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
   They are utterly indifferent to peace in Korea and the security of the nation.     they are interested only in flattering foreign forces, remaining in power and killing fellow countrymen with their help. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
   Such practices can be done only by sycophants, traitors and colonial war servants.

WPK is invincible
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Pyongyang, October 8 (KCNA) -- Foreign political figures admired the Workers' Party of Korea for developing into an invincible revolutionary party which  has struck roots deep among the popular masses and carrying on the socialist cause with credit.
   Hannu Harju, chairman of the for peace and socialism-the Communist Workers' Party of Finland, said that the WPK which has struck roots deep in the hearts of the Korean people  is enjoying absolute support from them for providing them with sovereignty, independence and national rights. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
   Angel Castro Lavarello, president of the national executive committee of the Left Revolutionary Union of Peru, noted that the WPK enjoys the  highest authority in the world for its Juche idea, organizing ability and close relationship  with the popular masses. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
   V. Tyulkin, first secretary of the central committee of the Communist Workers' Party of Russia, stressed that the WPK has convincingly led the struggle to defend and complete socialism under the leadership of the respected Kim Jong Il. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;        Joao Amazonas, chairman of the central committee of the Brazilian Communist Party, said that the WPK has enjoyed absolute support from the Korean people and  had the great international authority for its standing in the van of their struggle for socialism. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
   Claudio Campos, secretary general of the October 8 Revolutionary Movement of Brazil,  stressed that the  history of the WPK is a history of victory in the revolutionary struggle for independence, progress and the people's happiness.

Chinese Foreign Minister feted
 &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Pyongyang, October 8 (KCNA) -- The North Hamgyong Provincial People's Committee hosted a reception on October 7 in honour of the Chinese Foreign Minister and his party.
   Pak Su Gil, chairman of the committee, said in his address that North Hamgyong Province neighbouring  with Jilin Province of China is adding luster to the history of Korea-China friendship, cooperating with Chinese comrades and helping each other at the time of hardships. 
   The Chinese people made great achievements in the struggle to build a modernized  socialist country with self-reliance  and working hard and to reunify the whole country in the past five decades under the leadership of the Communist Party of China, he said, and noted: &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
   The Korean people wish the Chinese people greater success in their efforts to carry through the tasks  set forth at the 15th Congress of the Communist Party of China and the second session of the ninth National People's Congress.  &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
   Chinese Foreign Minister Tang Jiaxuan said in his speech that he came to feel more keenly the value of Sino-Korea friendship by participating in celebrations of the 50th anniversary of the establishment of diplomatic relations between china and the DPRK. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
   The people in North Hamgyong Province have made great achievements in socialist construction in the spirit of self-reliance and working hard under the leadership of General Secretary Kim Jong Il in recent years, he said. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
   He expressed the belief that the people in North Hamgyong Province would overcome the temporary difficulties in their advance and build their hometowns more beautifully. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
   Noting that North Hamgyong Province has friendly relations with Jilin and Heilongjiang provinces and is developing exchange and cooperation, he hoped that the traditional friendly relations of both sides will grow stronger and develop.

Monolithic unity of Korea lauded
 &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Pyongyang, October 8 (KCNA) -- Prof. of Catania University of Italy Amata, chief of the Catania branch of the Italian Committee for the Study of the Juche Idea, released a statement on September 27 in the countdown to the 2nd anniversary of the great leader Kim Jong Il's election as General Secretary of the Workers' Party of Korea and the 54th WPK birthday.
   The statement said: &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
   Today the international communist and labour movement is undergoing grave trials due to the persistent anti-socialist moves of the imperialists and betrayal of the contemporary revisionists. but I am convinced that the movement will surely emerge victorious, meeting their challenges. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
   It is because the movement is guided by the Juche idea fathered by the great leader President Kim Il Sung and the Workers' Party of Korea under the distinguished guidance of the supreme leader Kim Jong Il is standing in the van of the world revolution. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
   What has propelled the WPK to defend socialism and emerge victorious is the singlehearted unity of the leader, the party and the popular masses. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
   This unity of Korea is the source of inexhaustible strength that makes it possible for the whole party and all the people to fight for the final victory of socialism, rallied close around their leader.

Murder of South Koreans by U.S. troops
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Pyongyang, October 8 (KCNA) -- The U.S. imperialist aggressors brutally massacred civilians not only in Yongdong, North Chungchong Province, and Masan, South Kyongsang Province, but also in Changnyong and Sachon, South Kyongsang Province, and Jochiwon, South Chungchong Province, in the summer of 1950, according to a report from Seoul.
   The South Korean Ryonhap News  on October 5  quoted residents in Yocho-ri, Changnyong-up, Changnyong county, as saying that a group of the U.S. imperialist aggression troops  fired at citizens and burnt over 40 houses, leaving over 80 of them dead and fired shells upon the village in early august 1950. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
   Bombers of the U.S. imperialist troops strafed Jojang-ri, Konmyong-myon, Sachon on August 1, 1950, killing over 60 villagers and wounding over 20 others. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
   A radio of South Korea said that the U.S. imperialist aggression troops  captured and killed over 30 civilians, passing by Jochiwon, South Chungchong Province, on July 11, 1950 and ordered South Korean soldiers to carry away the dead bodies, before disappearing.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
   It was disclosed by a survivor over 70 who was shot and wounded at that time.

Okhodong sanatorium
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Pyongyang, October 8 (KCNA) -- The Okhodong sanatorium is located in the valley of Okhodong in Yaksu-ri, Sonchon county, North Phyongan Province.
   The treatment is mainly done by mineral water which was discovered more than 500 years ago, combined with mud available in the tidal flat along the West Sea and traditional Korean medicines.
   This method of treatment is particularly good in curing chronic diseases, including digestive, urinary and genital troubles. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
   The sanatorium is furnished with all facilities needed in drinking the gushing mineral water, cleansing stomach and intestines, taking bath in the mineral water, and administering treatment by mud, ultra-short and medium waves and paraffins. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
   Clinical practices are applied to the treatment of cardiovascular system disorders through the bath in mineral water, the treatment of asthma of trachea by mineral water and in the treatment of digestive trouble by mud. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
   All necessary amenities and services are available and good mountain-climbing may be obtained at the sanatorium.

Nat'l  meeting to celebrate Kim Jong Il's election as G.S. of WPK 
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Pyongyang, October 8 (KCNA) -- The second anniversary of the leader Kim Jong Il's election as General Secretary of the Workers' Party of Korea on October 8, Juche 86 (1997) is significantly celebrated in Korea.
   His election is a political event of epochal significance in the  development of the WPK and revolution. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;   
  A national meeting was held at the 6,000-seat theatre of the April 25 House of Culture in Pyongyang amid colorful functions being held. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
   At the meeting attended by Kim Yong Nam and other senior party and state officials, working people from all walks of life and soldiers of the Korean People's Army, Jon Pyong Ho, secretary of the WPK central committee,  made a report titled "The WPK  headed by the great Kim Jong Il will be ever-victorious." &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
   The reporter referred to the immortal exploits performed by Kim Jong Il for the fatherland and revolution, leading the WPK. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
   The campaign for modelling the whole party after the Juche idea has been vigorously conducted under his energetic leadership. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
   He has brought about a revolutionary  change in the organizational and ideological building of the party and in the building of leadership art, so that the WPK has become the revolutionary party  of Juche-type named after the great leader Kim Il Sung. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
   He built the WPK as the experienced and tested party which leads the revolution and construction to victory in any adversity and as the powerful guiding political organization which brilliantly  hews out a new era of the Juche revolution, breathing and moving in the leader's idea and intention, forming an integral whole with the masses and smashing all rigorous challenges of history. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;  
   He penetrated deep into the circumstances peculiar to the Korean revolution  which has to defend and accomplish the socialist cause in the fierce political and military confrontation with the imperialists, established the specific political formula of giving priority to military affairs, strengthened the national power of our country as a whole and demonstrated the dignity and might of Juche Korea to the world. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
   He has victoriously led the "arduous march" and the forced march to the second grand Chollima march and placed our country among the ranks of space powers, laying a credible springboard for building a powerful nation. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
    He saw to it that the Juche character and national character of the revolution and construction  have been adhered to as the fundamental principle to create historical miracles in the accomplishment of the socialist cause of Juche. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
   Always finding himself among the people and sharing life and death, sweets and bitters with them throughout his whole life, he made a revolutionary history of on-the-spot guidance unprecedented in history by visiting a total of 7,400 units, making a long journey of more than 300,000 kilometers over the past 35 years.
   His most pure and ardent loyalty to the idea and cause of the leader is the main source of the greatness and invincibility of Marshal Kim Jong Il's politics and leadership. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
   All the landmarks and dazzling changes of Korea vividly prove the respected Kim Jong Il is the most outstanding leader and the greatest statesman of the present era. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
   The Workers' Party of Korea enjoys the unquestioned dignity and authority  as it has the ever-victorious iron-willed brilliant  commander Kim Jong Il, the great master of thought and theory of our era and veteran of the world politics, as its general secretary, and the prospect of the Korean revolution is rosy.
